fields.bodyText: Armistice, 1918 is today's picture from the past Here's a beautiful entry for our GuardianWitness assignment: networks One of our most unusual photo galleries in a while is this set of images by Nancy Rica Schiff on some of the world's oddest jobs. Click here to see more. Today's Eyewitness is an apocalyptic view from the heart of the typhoon-devastated Philippines. Here's how you can help.
